<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>7-Day Escalation — Freeze Request {{ case_id }}</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px;color:#111;line-height:1.5">

<p>{{ issuer_contact_name or "Compliance team" }},</p>

<p>
  This is a formal seven-day escalation on the freeze request below.
  We have received no acknowledgement of any kind in
  <strong>{{ days_since_sent }} days</strong> since the original
  request was transmitted on {{ sent_at_human }} UTC.
</p>

<table style="border-collapse:collapse;width:100%;font-size:14px;margin:18px 0;background:#fef3c7;padding:12px;border:1px solid #d97706;border-radius:4px">
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#92400e;width:40%"><strong>Case</strong></td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0"><strong>{{ case_id }}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#92400e">Target wallet</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0;font-family:monospace">{{ target_address }}</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#92400e">Asset</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0">{{ asset_symbol }}{% if chain %} on {{ chain }}{% endif %}</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#92400e">Amount</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0"><strong>USD {{ requested_freeze_usd_human }}</strong></td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#92400e">First contact</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0">{{ sent_at_human }} UTC (no response)</td></tr>
  <tr><td style="padding:6px 0;color:#92400e">First follow-up</td>
      <td style="padding:6px 0">{{ last_followup_sent_at_human }} UTC (no response)</td></tr>
</table>

<p>
  Continued non-response materially increases the risk of fund
  dissipation through downstream conversion. The on-chain trace
  associated with this case has been preserved as evidence; if
  this request is not acted upon and the assets subsequently
  move off-platform, we will be required to document the
  non-response timeline in any subsequent law-enforcement
  filing.
</p>

{% if letter_language == "le_backed" or ic3_case_id %}
<p>
  <strong>This request carries law-enforcement backing.</strong>
  {% if ic3_case_id %}IC3 reference: <strong>{{ ic3_case_id }}</strong>.{% endif %}
  We anticipate that the responsible federal authority will
  follow up directly via subpoena should the informal channel
  produce no result within the next seven days.
</p>
{% endif %}

<p>
  Please confirm receipt at your earliest convenience. If this
  matter has been routed within your organization, a single-line
  acknowledgement of the receiving party is sufficient at this
  stage.
</p>

<p style="margin-top:24px">
  Regards,<br/>
  <strong>{{ investigator_name }}</strong><br/>
  {{ investigator_entity }}<br/>
  {{ investigator_email }}
</p>

<hr style="border:none;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;margin:24px 0">

<p style="font-size:12px;color:#6b7280">
  This is the third contact regarding case {{ case_id }} (original
  freeze request {{ sent_at_human }}; 72-hour follow-up
  {{ last_followup_sent_at_human }}). A fourteen-day escalation
  may trigger law-enforcement coordination if no response is
  received.
</p>

</body>
</html>
